data.description: Welcome home to 3520 Elm Avenue -- a cozy gem situated conveniently in the heart of Castle Shannon, walking distance to the trolley and a stone throw to numerous restaurants, shops, entertainment, fuel, and groceries. 20 minutes to downtown Pittsburgh. Enjoy the upcoming cool nights at the backyard fire pit or on your covered front porch. You'll be delighted by the high ceilings, generous room sizes, and by the updated full bath. Brand new metal roof installed in 2022. Brand new updated electrical throughout the entire home. New paint and flooring. Multi-use room off the kitchen is a perfect laundry space and can easily become a half bath. Large attached garage allows for storage galore! The main bedroom features dual, extra deep closets AND an adorable reading nook. This home was loved by its current owners for 32 years and has so much more love to give. You don't want to miss out on this solid home that's just waiting for your personal touches!
